headline: Cracker Barrel co-founder, 93, blasts $7M/year CEO’s ‘pitiful’ rebrand fail, work with Taco Bell. Is that unfair?
summary: He built the first Cracker Barrel in 1969. Now he says its future is at risk under new leadership.

headline: McDonald's And Microsoft Among 12 Companies To Announce Annual Increases In September
summary: August saw strong dividend growth, but September will likely bring modest hikes from long-time growers like Altria, Dover, and AWR. See why streaks will continue.
